== Xirbi Mhoji Gai Ga Zotaku Bori ==

My white cow is good to plough


Type: Dulpod

Source: A. da Gama/ C. Xavier. Goemchim Gitam. Mandde anim Dulpodam.Nr. 

Translated by: Alfred Noronha, Panaji, Ilhas, Goa, 30.05.2005



Xirbi mhoji gai ga zotaku bori,

My white cow is good to plough

Zotu ano taxita ga kombea sadari. (bis)

I don the plough at the crowing of the cock at sunrise (bis)

